# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Delivery Tracker OpenEnv Benchmark — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# All variables have sensible defaults hardcoded in inference.py,
# so this file is only needed if you want to override them.

# ── HuggingFace Inference API (default) ──────────────────────────
# The HF token is embedded in inference.py by default.
# Set these to override:
HF_TOKEN=your_token_here
API_BASE_URL=https://api-inference.huggingface.co/v1
MODEL_NAME=mistralai/Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.3

# ── Alternative: OpenAI API ──────────────────────────────────────
# Uncomment to use OpenAI instead of HuggingFace:
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# API_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
# MODEL_NAME=gpt-4o

# ── Health check server (Docker) ─────────────────────────────────
PORT=7860
